  • Possession of Controlled Substance Heroin, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(b).
  • Possession of Controlled Substance Heroin, an unclassified misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 961.41(3g)(b).
